{"word":"G1983 - ἐπισκοπέω - episkopéō - ep-ee-skop-eh'-o - Look diligently","slug":"G1983","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπισκοπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>episkopéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-ee-skop-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Look diligently"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - episkopeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ep-ee-skop-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G4648\">G4648</a>; to <i>oversee</i>; by implication to <i>beware:</i> - look diligently, take the oversight."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1980\">G1980</a>, <a href=\"#/G1984\">G1984</a>, <a href=\"#/G244\">G244</a>"}]}